Text: In-State Tuition and Residency F-1 and J-1 students and scholars are classified as non-immigrant immigration statuses. As such, F-1 and J-1 status holders are not eligible for in-state tuition. For more information on residency, eligibility for in-state tuition and related matters, please contact the Registrar’s Office. - https://registrar.umbc.edu/services/residency/
